1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,400
What if I told you two different organisms can become one?

2
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:08,000
Meet lichen, a remarkable partnership between fungi and algae.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:12,800
The fungi provide structure and protection, while algae produce food through photosynthesis.

4
00:00:12,800 --> 00:00:17,600
Together, they can survive in extreme environments—rocky surfaces, deserts, even the Arctic!

5
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:22,800
But here’s the catch—scientists are still unraveling the full extent of this collaboration.

6
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:24,800
Curious about more science mysteries?

